-08-31T16:00:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">BNO平權聯署要人呀！！仲差二萬三千幾人！多你一個係好多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論你續領左未都要簽，唔好辜負黃婆婆揮舞英國旗既努力。<br />\n<br />\nPostcode寫00000或者852<br />\n地區揀香港<br />\n<br />\n聯署網址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=2d6837c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n做完立即廣傳轉發比朋友，係要一傳十，十傳百，快、快、快!<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d72e5d9a49589958f9db849ff3f38efd1ad8a9af","tid":1514841,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacf13c0eb2a01e9044901234a04f5eab2eea00f","tid":1514841,"uid":308875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T09:22:52.000Z","msg":"光復香港, 不要支籍<br />\n&ldquo;中國單方面宣稱中英聯合聲明已經失效，香港人該何去何從？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n用1分鐘嘅時間簽名，務求收集到10萬簽名將BNO平權議題推上議會討論<br />\n註: 轉BC後可傳俾97後<br />\n為咗你自己，仲有你嘅摯愛，簽名？刻不容緩<br />\n<br />\nPostal Code 請填000000，如果身處英國就填所在地點嘅Code<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=2d6837c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"1d67941a970b9981a4d47517c0a2faa4a42d0730","tid":1514841,"uid":19037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"